{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"45424-ebar-hahachun","title":"এবাৰ  হাঁহাচোন","description":"হৰিণা পোৱালিটোৰ পিছে পিছে তাৰ বন্ধুবোৰ দৌৰি আছিল ।","language":"Assamese","langCode":"as","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Rupali Saikia ( Tamuli  )"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"North East Educational Trust","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/45424-ebar-hahachun"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721917/size3/548c488c38612955cf9c42fe6894c5f1.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721917/size6/548c488c38612955cf9c42fe6894c5f1.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14/size6/faa10856c7c9b841685389bc1904a89b.jpg","text":"এখন হাবিত এটা হৰিণা পোৱালি দৌৰি আছিল ।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/15/size6/536bf872a08ea48e3feec9063b7541fc.jpg","text":"সি শহাটোতকৈ আগত আছিল ।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/16/size6/3881ed85209ed203262e37a1a9237419.jpg","text":"সি হাতীতকৈয়ো আগত আছিল ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/17/size6/c5a5a22c02fbb31c649a73f27e8966eb.jpg","text":"জাঁপ মাৰি সি জুৰিটো পাৰ হ’ল ।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/18/size6/afee5a4da085394d44070fd330c4d178.jpg","text":"সি ভগা বেৰাখনো দৌৰি পাৰ হৈ গ’ল ।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/19/size6/14b4db70d06071c4e9c843e2bac3c296.jpg","text":"সি দৌৰি থকা ঘাঁহনি ডৰাত এটা ডাঙৰ শিল পৰি আছিল । সেই শিলটোত খুন্দা খাই হৰিণা পোৱালিটো বাগৰি পৰিল ।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/20/size6/37361c6a3d23feb30eaf9dd9e66e4fa0.jpg","text":"পৰি যোৱাত বৰ দুখ পাই সি কান্দিবলৈ ধৰিলে ।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/21/size6/c6dd7e9100c59475dfff669aea42043c.jpg","text":"বান্দৰ এটা আহি তাৰ ভৰিটো মালিচ কৰি দিলেহি । হৰিণা পোৱালিটোৰ চকুৰ পৰা পানী ওলাবলৈ ধৰিলে ।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/22/size6/b7c5a2321034eefd58064417dbed109c.jpg","text":"ভালুক ককায়ে আহি তাক কোলাত তুলি ল’লে । তথাপিও হৰিণা পোৱালিটোৱে কান্দিবলৈ নেৰিলে ।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/23/size6/4b9d3c5ef3ff7f193bbc57ee9873948a.jpg","text":"এইবাৰ তাৰ মাক আহিল । মাকে ক’লে, “শিলটোক বৰ দুষ্ট, তাক আমি মাৰি দিম ।\"","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/24/size6/fa745053851dd15865fd30a47599ad37.jpg","text":"হৰিণা পোৱালিটোৱে ক’লে, “নাই মা, তাক নামাৰিবা । তাক মাৰিলে সিও কান্দিবলৈ আৰম্ভ কৰিব ।\" তাৰ কথা শুনি মাকে হাঁহিলে, হৰিণা পোৱালীটোৱেও হাঁহিবলৈ ধৰিলে ।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":133}}